{"tid":1873763,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"［人命關天］住緊舊式公屋低層，平時樓上沖廁間唔中有臭味","createTime":"2020-02-10T21:45:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T21:59:32.000Z","uid":138724,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"834fb6f3474323be3da90f836cb24e2be090c1d8","tid":1873763,"uid":138724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T21:45:03.000Z","msg":"認真post<br />\n<br />\n如題，舊式公屋，近走廊個頭有百葉窗個隻，廚房同廁所喺陽台（應該算係）<br />\n<br />\n住緊極低層，個廁所就間歇性有臭味，一日十幾廿次，有時嚴重嘅話，廁所門唔關嘅話就客廳甚至睡房都會聞到有味<br />\n<br />\n而個馬桶有時會有d咁嘅白色不明野郁郁下（非我地依戶嘅精液<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw兩年前好似搵過d房屋署定係咩部門嘅人上黎check<br />\n最後好似話搞唔到定check 唔到問題就不了了之<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n尋晚有新聞話武漢肺炎有可能會靠屎喉傳染<br />\n我依個case會唔會好嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋主要想問兩樣野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1.應唔應該即刻暫時搬走暫時避下風頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.長遠黎講依個問題有無得fix<span style=\"font-size: small;\">如果有命淨</span>, 同埋成日咁臭係咩成因"},{"pid":"38e553b46e808e690ca4ace2dab3a7b5df778abf","tid":1873763,"uid":23445,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T21:50:17.000Z","msg":"租一年service apartment/酒店保平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d33f3d4e1ce9b317da25832e0946d776aebc7a","tid":1873763,"uid":138724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38e553b46e808e690ca4ace2dab3a7b5df778abf","tid":1873763,"uid":23445,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T21:50:17.000Z","msg":"租一年service apartment/酒店保平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T21:53:43.000Z","msg":"考慮緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但都想聽專業人士分析下"},{"pid":"ffc28b162810f818cf170423dd7913ab0dadb263","tid":1873763,"uid":51755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T21:54:38.000Z","msg":"擺部cam影住個馬桶觀察佢點形成"},{"pid":"e8e08d9268274cf1346977a37ab2e458d43ebed7","tid":1873763,"uid":25212,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T21:58:31.000Z","msg":"你要留意下上面沖水你個馬桶水位有無升降，有無小水泉，如果有你/大廈既氣喉可能塞了/唔適合"},{"pid":"a32b3f18843df4f20f96cb24b5ef373866d5440f","tid":1873763,"uid":138724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ffc28b162810f818cf170423dd7913ab0dadb263","tid":1873763,"uid":51755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T21:54:38.000Z","msg":"擺部cam影住個馬桶觀察佢點形成"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T21:59:32.000Z","msg":"團野好忽然，一兩個星期先發現到1次<br />\n又唔太似氣體，但又郁下郁下咁"}]}